Class CDTest

java.lang.Object
CDTest
public class CDTest extends Object
Unit tests for the CD class.

Ensures that all constructors correctly initialize the state and that overridden methods from the Media superclass return the expected values specific to a CD.

      @Test void testShortConstructor_initialValuesCorrect()
      Verifies that the simplified constructor initializes fields with default values.

      Specifically checks that:

      • Title, Artist, and ISBN are set correctly.
      • Status defaults to "Available".
      • Copy ID defaults to 1.
